# ng-alain Theme Customization Standards

> **Related Rules**: See [Styling Standards](./styling.mdc), [Accessibility Standards](./accessibility.mdc)

## Theme Tool Usage

- Use `yarn color-less` to generate color palettes
- Use `yarn theme` to generate theme CSS
- Use theme variables consistently

## Color System

- Use theme variables for colors
- Ensure color contrast meets WCAG 2.1 AA (see [Accessibility](./accessibility.mdc))
- Define custom colors in theme configuration

## Theme Variables

- Use ng-alain theme variables
- Override variables in custom theme file
- Keep theme customization maintainable

